<paragraph id="5F9A8E2B91821F4488765FBB167C969A" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Ajax-Rittersporn</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="76CA59A8C3E14C7EF3F7320CEC747BDB" pageId="null" pageNumber="30" type="description">
<paragraph id="6D44E9FC896B6BAFB4771EBD1553435A" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<emphasis id="D1A454C6A33B636CEF3E777A66D6547D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
D. 
<taxonomicName id="2DB4C36E621561A74E46BBC3B1EB90C3" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Consolida" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="30" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Consolida</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
(Nr. 3) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="992CB72443F8DAE3103AF4F2F317CCA7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Blattabschnitte stets fiederteilig;</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="00C32171CE3A53EBEC293643E50FBF0F" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Blueten</normalizedToken>
oft in dichteren Trauben; 
<emphasis id="CA45DDB175DC5E3A124DF15AE8E6E0AD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Fruchtknoten behaart.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="2986822A25134388B2649DF8885CCCCF" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4D72F191123C3939376589FC103D9574" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis id="8791902C29BE9883D7A584DFE1CF24C9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="B3B381EA418784A82FA5803123C03645" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">16:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="70B1E11AAA2D9C885D262CDD6C25AA0D" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Langlet 1927, Gregory 1941), keine zytologischen 
<normalizedToken id="2E5E6F9976E2D161773D1335D660F567" originalValue="Abnormitäten" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Abnormitaeten</normalizedToken>
in Pollenmeiose (Tjebbes 1927); weitere 
<normalizedToken id="B023DEAB02B4409D4F7EA202B9113B4F" originalValue="übereinstimmende" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">uebereinstimmende</normalizedToken>
Angaben in 
<normalizedToken id="66E76BC8CEDFFAE21F7B3723D9602881" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="F02E3B17D31DF6DC252D32748A44068C" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Loeve</normalizedToken>
(1961).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B9C8A68BE3B0A6A380ABA0C9FA299BB" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis id="134091DD725FA92C0FD5F4FE7E4B45ED" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie 
<emphasis id="A65AA9933DC253964D6C283BDB53A6A4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
D. 
<taxonomicName id="417A15FDEDDD1603552D4F3FEE3C3EED" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Consolida" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="30" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Consolida</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
, jedoch meist nur an 
<normalizedToken id="D22FAECCE032337FB1A38098F2E325DD" originalValue="Wegrändern" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Wegraendern</normalizedToken>
und an unbebauten Orten.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AFA96E85A13F1C2704A3AC85D9409CCB" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis id="A4F4DB287F451B67840C0A2FEA564C88" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="64C1228DB3E2BE789EB7D642FAE97F34" originalValue="Südeuropa" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Suedeuropa</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="01DCB7576CC2CFDAAD76DBDE7DE20C79" originalValue="Südwestasien" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Suedwestasien</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="82C0359808CFE8B883059F2E695FD63D" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis ins aralo-kaspische Gebiet), Nordwestafrika. In Mitteleuropa und Nordamerika als Gartenpflanze 
<normalizedToken id="49F2589754A905634566E7216AEDA42D" originalValue="eingeführt" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">eingefuehrt</normalizedToken>
und verwildert. - Im Gebiet viel seltener als 
<emphasis id="D808D54E6E573E603A06D2065861E499" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
D. 
<taxonomicName id="5F91FF833D71C3B71593970D24505989" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Consolida" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="30" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Consolida</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BE3539A61A387C6EEF8394F5DE1A0115" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis id="B1CE51CB535A3870309154606EFE9850" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Nach Zimmermann (1966) ist 
<taxonomicName id="8B56186DBF583741B2C2B29AD6C9F05B" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Consolida" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="30" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ajacis">
<emphasis id="34D2AFD16BCFE244D0B77FC5A3F0ED6E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">D. Ajacis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
nicht identisch mit 
<taxonomicName id="1AAF4D35CA14FD71515C79BC443F6FF4" authority="L." authorityName="L." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" genus="Delphinium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="30" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ambiguum">
<emphasis id="6C2F67266DE53DC2F433B32C946E97FA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">D. ambiguum</emphasis>
<authorityName id="31DC96A3902728B1E1D22496C630CB93" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">L.</authorityName>
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
